node.title: Teens hospitalised after shark attack during evening swim
node.alt: One of the beaches at Ocean Grove
node.description: A Victorian beach remains closed this morning after a shark attack on Monday night left two teens injured.
node.content: ["A Victorian beach remains closed this morning after a shark attack on Monday night left two teens injured.", "The girl, 15, and boy, 16, were bitten while swimming at the Ocean Grove Beach, near Geelong,\u00a0near dusk.", "The pair was taken to Geelong Hospital for treatment and were in a stable condition.", "Locals said the girl was bitten on the lower leg by a reef shark in shallow water.", "The boy came to her rescue and was also bitten when he tried to fight off the shark.", "Onlookers provided first aid to the pair.", "The Victorian Fisheries Authority said the shark had been sighted close to shore and urged people to report any further sightings by calling triple-0."]
